Preheat the oven to 180C/350F/Gas 4.Crack the eggs into a large bowl and beat well. Add the pasta and herbs, season well with salt and freshly ground black pepper and stir well.Heat the butter in a small ovenproof frying pan, pour in the egg and pasta mixture and cook for 3-4 minutes, until set and lightly browned on the bottom.Place in the oven and cook for 3-4 minutes, or until cooked through.To serve, slide onto a plate and cut into slices.